    <h3>About<strong> SpaceX</strong></h3>
    <p>
        SpaceX is a private aerospace company that designs, constructs, and launches spacecraft and rockets.
        SpaceX is a young and very accomplished company being well-known for their successful attempts at returning multiple spacecrafts from a low Earth orbit.
        Through their innovation and accomplishments, SpaceX was able to obtain contracts for other notable companies such as the National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) and Blue Origin.
        [<a href="https://www.spacex.com/about">REF</a>]
    </p>
