            <h3>The Starman</h3>
            <p>
                Starman was a publicity stunt from SpaceX that included a mannequin wearing a space suit, a Tesla car, and a Falcon Heavy rocket.
                SpaceX placed the mannequin with the space suit into the car and launched it using the Falcon Heavy rocket.
                Now the car is orbiting around the sun, in space, just like the Earth does.
            </p>
            <p> For more information and the tracking of Starman, please see <a href="https://spacein3d.com/starman">"Where is Starman?"</a></p>
